(192, 1, '2014-07-04 08:56:36', '2014-07-04 08:56:36', 'The neoprene scopecoat is constructed of high quality 5mm thick neoprene laminated with nylon. It''s simple design safeguards any kind of scope from dings and scratches, dust, dirt and moisture. Neoprene has a 5% moisture absorbency, which pulls moisture away from the scope and helps protect it from rust and corrosion. Built by Scopecoat for Hunt The Distance.', 'Neoprene Scope Coat', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'neoprene-scope-coat', '', '', '2014-07-07 11:15:22', '2014-07-07 11:15:22', '', 0, 'http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/?post_type=product&#038;p=192', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(194, 1, '2014-07-04 09:04:49', '2014-07-04 09:04:49', 'The one-piece construction of the Talley Lightweight Alloy Scope Mount is unique.  The rigid design has no joint between the scope and the rifle.  The Talley Lightweight unitized design eliminates the possibility of an "out of alignment" interface or "loose connection" between the ring and base that can occur with traditional two-piece designs.\r\nUltimately this provides more strength and durability than rival steel rings and bases, but doing it with a lighter overall weight.  By extruding the 7000 series alloy, known for its durability, and then precision CNC machining the mount to its final design we can provide you with the strongest, lightest mount system on the market.', 'Talley Lightweight Rings', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'talley-lightweight-rings', '', '', '2014-07-07 11:16:54', '2014-07-07 11:16:54', '', 0, 'http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/?post_type=product&#038;p=194', 0, 'product', '', 0),
