(264, 1, '2014-07-08 09:05:31', '2014-07-08 09:05:31', '<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-lg-12">\r\n<h1>NightForce G7 Scopes</h1>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-189" style="border: solid 8px #666;" src="http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/p-img4.png" alt="p-img4" width="335" height="215" /><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-191" style="border: solid 8px #666; margin-left: 20px;" src="http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/p-image5.png" alt="p-image5" width="335" height="215" />\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">With tactical tasks in mind, these manufactured by Nightforce Optics rifle scopes bring some more custom features which any user – hunter, long range bench rest shooter or military sniper can really enjoy.</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">G7 scopes come with famous G7 ballistic compensation technology and fully customized ballistic match turret adjustment knob. Scope reticle give shooter opportunity make fast, simple and precise ballistic compensation while shooting, depending on used ammo and weather state.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>BR II Rangefinder</h3>\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">With Nightforce Optics strict control and tests system, G7 rifle scope equipped with cemented lens assembly, meet every important standard which mean solid and rugged rifle scope with excellent repeatability shoot after shoot. For low light performance The G7 BR2 (Ballistic Rangefinder 2000) rangefinder has achieved the most significant milestone in laser rangefinder technology since their introduction to the hunting industry. The BR2 model is the first rangefinder to feature a real time ballistic calculation that accepts your specific bullet Ballistic Coefficient and Muzzle Velocity as inputs to build a custom ballistic profile, and then calculate a real time ballistic solution.</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">The impressive ranging capability comes from Laser Technologies Inc, one of the world’s premier professional measurement companies. New developments in sensor technology along with dozens of other patented technologies give the G7 BR2 eye safe ranging capabilities beyond 2000 yards.</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">By utilizing the G7 ballistic engine, the G7 BR2 is able to utilize measurements of line of sight range, incline angle, and air density to make a complete ballistic calculation of the Shoot To range for your custom bullet drop compensating reticle or turret. “Just range it and dial it” has never been so simple or precise.</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">scope has high quality lens system, matched and tuned by hands of experienced engineer to provide the highest optical performance ever possible.</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;"></p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;"></p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: center;"><a href="http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/product-category/scope/">SEE ALL SCOPES</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'NIGHTFORCE G7 SCOPES/RANGEFINDERS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nightforce-g7-scopesrangefinders', '', '', '2014-07-22 20:00:23', '2014-07-22 20:00:23', '', 0, 'http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/?page_id=264', 0, 'page', '', 0),
