(313, 1, '2014-07-22 19:57:18', '2014-07-22 19:57:18', '<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-lg-12">\r\n<h1>Huskemaw</h1>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-182" style="border: solid 8px #666;" src="http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/p-img1.png" alt="p-img1" width="335" height="215" /><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-186" style="border: solid 8px #666; margin-left: 20px;" src="http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/p-imag2.png" alt="p-imag2" width="335" height="215" />\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-187" style="border: solid 8px #666; margin-top: 30px;" src="http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/p-img3.png" alt="p-img3" width="335" height="215" />\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">With technical advancements like True BC, the Rapid Field Ballistic Compensator and the simple yet powerful Hunt Smart range finding and windage compensating reticle. The 30mm main tube, 50mm objective lens, and side focus parallax correction dial make the Huskemaw LR scopes an outstanding choice for both varmint hunters and target shooters. It also includes special features for the big game hunter. Ballistic compensation and parallax adjustments are easily made without breaking shooting position, and the 42mm or 50mm objective lens'' create a bright, clear image for high magnification and low light use.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Features</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Windage Compensation Technology</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">True BC Drop Compensation</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Hunt Smart Reticle</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">30mm Maintube</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Fast Focus Eyepiece</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Full Lifetime Guarantee</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/product-category/scope/">SEE ALL SCOPES</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'HUSKEMAW SCOPES', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '262-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-07-22 19:57:18', '2014-07-22 19:57:18', '', 262, 'http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/262-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
