(334, 1, '2014-07-19 05:30:51', '2014-07-19 05:30:51', '<h1>Twisted Custom with steel barrel      <a class="buy-link" href="../../product/twisted-custom-steel-barrel/">Buy Now</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="buy-price">$5,100.00</span></h1>\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">Our twisted custom line of rifles offer the traditional hunting looks with a twist. These rifles are crafted with no b.s. approach. The parts that are used to assemble these rifles are top notch in all means. This custom line is designed for the shooter/hunter that wants to squeeze all the accuracy possible out of a rifle. Our goal with this gun is to make a awesome shooting rifle and not worry about the weight as much.</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">This rifle we used our custom steel action it is a top of the line strictest tolerances possible held from high end cnc machines. Through this process it eliminates the worrying of loosing accuracy to sloppy tolerances. These actions come completely trued and will allow to squeeze the maximum amount of accuracy out of the rifle with least amount of effort. These actions use the M16 type extractor which provides reliable shell extraction. The bolt comes threaded for bolt knobs and we can even give you a more personalized touch with a custom knob design. With most barrel flute designs we can flute the bolt knob to match.</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">Only top notch products will do, so only top notch long range rifle stock will work and that is what is included. We have many different styles and makes of stocks that can be used on this rifle. All are long range hunting friendly wider forearms typically. This wider forearm will accept barrel contours up to sendero contour. This wider forearm is also a huge component in long range shooting from a stand point that the rifle will find a place to lay and recoil without twisting. This will provide more consistency and tighter groups. We have stock available for sporter to heavy contour barrel channels, and