(342, 1, '2014-07-19 05:32:45', '2014-07-19 05:32:45', '<h1>Remington Sendero Package          <a class="buy-link" href="../../product/sendero-package-7mm-mag-300-win-or-300-remington-ultra-mag/">Buy Now</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="buy-price">$4,500.00</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">We took the best shooting rifle out of the box and improved it. We took all the design flaws that we felt the sendero has and modified it to the rifle we were proud to carry. This system is a great turn-key system for someone that is wanting something quicker with conventional looks all for the lowest price possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">We took a sendero rifle and installed a muzzle brake, custom trigger set at 2# or your preferable hunting weight. Fully bed the action to remove any play from the one size fits all aluminum bedding block stock. Then mount the rings, and lap the rings to eliminate any bind that could cause the long range turret from working flawlessly and consistent every time. The rifle action will be leveled which will allow us to level the scope to ensure the two parts work as one. Then to eliminate the human factor the scope level will be installed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">Our next step is when we really go to town and make this system come to life. We will thoroughly clean and break in the rifle barrel. Do the load work-up to find a good long range load to make this gun your long range hunting buddy. But before that happens we have to shoot for drop charts to know your bullet trajectory to either have a custom turret made or enter your ballistics into your new rangefinder.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">Available in 7mm mag, 300 Win, or 300 Remington Ultra mag</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Features:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Trigger set at 2# or specified weight</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Brake (your choice side port or radial brake)</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Custom Bedding of the Action</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Huskemaw Blue Diamond 5-20x50mm</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Talley Lightweight Rings</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Scope Level Installed</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Rings Lapped, Scope Mounted, and Leveled</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Load Development</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Barrel Break-in</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Data Work</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Stock Protector</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Scope Coat</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Sendero Package (7mm mag, 300 Win, or 300 Remington Ultra mag)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sendero-package-7mm-mag-300-win-or-300-remington-ultra-mag', '', '', '2014-07-23 07:29:36', '2014-07-23 07:29:36', '', 223, 'http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/?page_id=342', 0, 'page', '', 0),
