(368, 1, '2014-07-21 04:28:13', '2014-07-21 04:28:13', '<strong>Twisted Titanium with steel barrel</strong>\r\n\r\nTwisted Titanium line of rifles will be the lightest weight and most beneficial for that hunter that wants to have a long range rifle but is a dedicated back country pack in hunter. It will not suffer anywhere for quality in components that could hinder long range hunting. Our primary components are action, stock and barrels that make a great long range rifle and as you read on, you will see we skimped NO WHERE.\r\n\r\nIn this rifle system we used one of our custom titanium actions. Titanium is very strong and comes in at about 42 percent the weight of steel and has a high strength to weight ratio. This make a perfect first choice when we were trying to cut weight and not sacrifice anything to durability. The titanium action is a component of weight loss taking away 6-8 ounces over a comparable steel action.\r\n\r\nFor this rifle to reduce weight we use our 100% carbon fiber rifle stock. This not only will cause a significant weight loss but remain rigged with a wider forearm. This wider forearm will accept barrel contours up to sendero contour. This wider forearm is also a huge component in long range shooting from a stand point that the rifle will find a place to lay and recoil without twisting. This will in the end will provide more consistency and tighter groups.\r\n\r\nA Fluted stainless steel barrel will be used in this package. Although the barrel will be steel that can add a little weight, we do flute the barrel to counter act the weight gain. This is a option that is usually based off of personal preference and what you believe gives your rifle the most "twisted " look. You may choose the steel option based off a twisted flute design or just because you like the traditional hunting rifle look. Either way rest assured it will meet your expectations when shooting and packing. Our custom barrels are crafted from the finest material made today, 416R Stainless Steel. They are pulled button-rifled, Double stressed relieved at the mill &amp; triple stress relieved.<em>. </em>Then each barrel is hand lapped with a uniform land and groove diameter, up to 0.0001" from breech to muzzle. Our barrels have the 5C rifling which contribute to <em>more velocity</em><strong>, </strong><em>great accuracy</em><strong>, </strong><em>longer barrel life</em><strong>, </strong><em>reduced bolt</em><em>pressure</em><strong> and </strong><em>ease in clean ability</em>. Along with all of this comes the twisted look, this is the fluting. We have many different designs of fluting that will just make you stand out from everyone else. The barrel length will be discussed but usually 26-28".\r\n\r\nAlong with the few main components these rifles will have a muzzle brake to reduce recoil, this will give you a choice of a side port brake or a radial brake. Also a custom trigger set at two pounds or desired weight. Action bedded, and we would even give you a free stock dipping and a cerekote to make your rifle more personalized and twisted. We will also include loads that will shoot .5 moa at 100 yards but prefer all rifles to go out the door with sub .5 moa loads. We also will not twist you around with the loads and use just any components. We only use long range hunting components, which are high ballistic coefficient bullets and temperature stable powder. Upon shipping the exact load will be included so you can duplicate it.\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\n\r\nThis package eligible for FREE optional Stock Dip &amp; FREE optional Cerekote\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Titanium Action (8oz or less, lighter)</li>\r\n	<li>Custom Steel Barrel 26-28".</li>\r\n	<li>Custom Twisted Barrel Fluting (8 flutes takes away approx. 8oz)</li>\r\n	<li>Custom Trigger set at 2# or specified weight</li>\r\n	<li>Custom Brake (your choice side port or radial brake)</li>\r\n	<li>Fully Carbon Stock</li>\r\n	<li>Custom Bedding of the Action</li>\r\n	<li>Caliber available but not limited to; 6.5-284, 7mm mag, 7mm-300 win, 300 win, 300 rum, 338 edge, 338 lapua improved and many more.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Twisted Titanium (Steel Barrel)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '330-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-21 04:28:13', '2014-07-21 04:28:13', '', 330, 'http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/330-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
