st any components. We only use long range hunting components, which are high ballistic coefficient bullets and temperature stable powder. Upon shipping the exact load will be included so you can duplicate it.\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Remington Action</li>\r\n	<li>Custom Steel Barrel 24-32"</li>\r\n	<li>Trigger set at 2# or specified weight</li>\r\n	<li>Brake (your choice side port or radial brake)</li>\r\n	<li>Action Fully Trued and Blueprinted</li>\r\n	<li>Long Range Hunting Stock</li>\r\n	<li>Custom Bedding of the Action</li>\r\n	<li>Caliber available but not limited to.6.5-284, 7mm mag, 7mm-300 win, 300 win, 300 rum, 338 edge, 338 lapua improved and many more.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Twisted Remington', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '340-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-21 04:32:12', '2014-07-21 04:32:12', '', 340, 'http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/340-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
