(372, 1, '2014-07-21 04:32:43', '2014-07-21 04:32:43', '<strong>Twisted Remington Deluxe</strong>\r\n\r\nThis line of rifles we used the tried and true Remington action. We use this action because of its proven performance around the world. The Remington action was so good almost all custom action manufactures cloned it for their design. We also like these actions because easily to acquire and unlimited parts available at almost any given moment. This action fit our rifle line so well because it is a clean canvas which leads to the most opportunities to create something truly twisted look. The bolt has not been fluted, the receiver has not been milled or fluted, we can skeletonize the bolt handle, install twisted bolt knob. All these features are not possible to get on a custom action. The one downside of having to true up and blue print these actions is more than worth it to get a truly one of a kind rifle.\r\n\r\nOnly top notch products will do, so only top notch long range rifle stock will work and that is what is included. We have many different styles and makes of stock s that can be used on this rifle. All are long range hunting friendly wider forearms typically. This wider forearm will accept barrel contours up to sendero contour. This wider forearm is also a huge component in long range shooting from a stand point that the rifle will find a place to lay and recoil without twisting. This will provide more consistency and tighter groups. We have stock available for sporter to heavy contour barrel channels, and vertical grips or standard.\r\n\r\nOur custom barrels are crafted from the finest material made today, 416R Stainless Steel. They are pulled button-rifled, Double stressed relieved at the mill &amp; triple stress relieved.<em>. </em>Then each barrel is hand lapped with a uniform land and groove diameter up to 0.0001" from breech to muzzle. Our barrels have the 5C rifling which contribute to <em>more velocity</em><strong>, </strong><em>great accuracy</em>