>Custom Bedding of the Action</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Caliber available but not limited to; 6.5-284, 7mm mag, 7mm-300 win, 300 win, 300 rum, 338 edge, 338 lapua improved and many more</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Twisted Custom (Steel Barrel)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '334-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-21 05:33:27', '2014-07-21 05:33:27', '', 334, 'http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/334-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
