(384, 1, '2014-07-21 05:46:15', '2014-07-21 05:46:15', '<h1>Twisted Remington</h1>\n\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">This rifle was designed for the hunters that need a serious rifle, that felt we didn''t cater to their traditional hunting rifle design needs. We did not skimp on anything that would cause the accuracy to suffer, but just kept it simple without the twisted add-ons. With this rifle line you can add options to it to make exactly what you want.</p>\n\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">Rifle stock, we have many different styles and makes of stock s that can be used on this rifle. All are long range hunting friendly wider forearm. This wider forearm will accept barrel contours up to sendero contour. This wider forearm is also a huge component in long range shooting from a stand point that the rifle will find a place to lay and recoil without twisting. This will provide more consistency and tighter groups. We have stock available for sporter to heavy contour barrel channels, and vertical grips or standard.</p>\n\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">Our custom barrels are crafted from the finest material made today, 416R Stainless Steel. They are pulled button-rifled, Double stressed relieved at the mill &amp; triple stress relieved. Then each barrel is hand lapped with a uniform land and groove diameter up to 0.0001" from breech to muzzle. Our barrels have the 5C rifling which contribute to more velocity, great accuracy, longer barrel life</em><strong>, </strong><em>reduced bolt</em><em>pressure</em><strong> and </strong><em>ease in cleaning ability</em>.</p>\n\nAlong with the few main components these rifles will have a muzzle brake to reduce recoil, this will give you a choice of a side port brake or a radial brake. Also a custom trigger set at two pounds or desired weight. Action fully bedded. We will also include loads that will shoot .5 moa at 100 yards but prefer all rifles to go out the door with sub .5 moa loads. We also will not twist you around with the loads and use just any components. We only use long range hunting components, which are high ballistic coefficient bullets and temperature stable powder. Upon shipping the exact load will be included so you can duplicate it.\n\nFeatures:\n<ul>\n	<li>Remington Action</li>\n	<li>Custom Steel Barrel 24-32"</li>\n	<li>Trigger set at 2# or specified weight</li>\n	<li>Brake (your choice side port or radial brake)</li>\n	<li>Action Fully Trued and Blueprinted</li>\n	<li>Long Range Hunting Stock</li>\n	<li>Custom Bedding of the Action</li>\n	<li>Caliber available but not limited to.6.5-284, 7mm mag, 7mm-300 win, 300 win, 300 rum, 338 edge, 338 lapua improved and many more.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;', 'Twisted Remington', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '340-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-07-21 05:46:15', '2014-07-21 05:46:15', '', 340, 'http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/340-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
