apua improved and many more.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;', 'Twisted Remington Deluxe', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '338-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-07-21 05:55:52', '2014-07-21 05:55:52', '', 338, 'http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/338-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
