ainless Steel. They are pulled button-rifled, Double stressed relieved at the mill &amp; triple stress relieved. Then each barrel is hand lapped with a uniform land and groove diameter up to 0.0001" from breech to muzzle. Our barrels have the 5C rifling which contribute to more velocity, great accuracy, longer barrel life, reduced bolt pressure and ease in cleaning ability. Along with all of this comes the twisted look, this is the fluting. We have many different designs of fluting that will just make you stand out from everyone else.</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">Along with the few main components these rifles will have a muzzle brake to reduce recoil, this will gi ve you a choice of a side port brake or a radial brake. Also a custom trigger set at two pounds or desired weight. Action bedded, and we would even give you a free stock dipping and a cerekote to make your rifle more personalized and twisted. We will also include loads that will shoot .5 moa at 100 yards but prefer all rifles to go out the door with sub .5 moa loads. We also will not twist you around with the loads and use just any components. We only use long range hunting components, which are high ballistic coefficient bullets and temperature stable powder. Upon shipping the exact load will be included so you can duplicate it.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Features:</h2>\r\n<p style="font-size: 18px;">This package eligible for FREE optional Stock Dip &amp; FREE optional Cerekote</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Custom Action</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Custom Steel Barrel 26-32"</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Custom Twisted Barrel Fluting</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Tactical Bolt Knob</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Custom Trigger set at 2# or specified weight</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Custom Brake (your choice side port or radial brake)</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Fully Carbon Stock</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Custom Bedding of the Action</li>\r\n	<li style="font-size: 18px;">Caliber available but not limited to; 6.5-284, 7mm mag, 7mm-300 win, 300 win, 300 rum, 338 edge, 338 lapua improved and many more</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Twisted Custom (Steel Barrel)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '334-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-22 06:05:48', '2014-07-22 06:05:48', '', 334, 'http://endtoenddesigns.com/huntthedistance/334-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
